{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-novel-version-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon; Novel Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-07",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/themaltesefalconnovel_2603_librivox/maltesefalcon_07_hammett_128kb.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "G in the Air",
  "reader_name": "NLizer",
  "page_num": 6,
  "page_total": 6,
  "page_start_sec": 1209.64,
  "page_end_sec": 1360.78,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.77,
  "corrected": "claude",
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 1209.64,
      "end": 1210.8,
      "text": "There's a way of figuring it.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1211.776,
      "end": 1212.1,
      "text": "\"Uh-huh.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1212.62,
      "end": 1214.48,
      "text": "I could've butchered Miles to get his wife"
    },
    {
      "start": 1214.66,
      "end": 1217.48,
      "text": "and then Thursby so I could hang Miles's killing on him."
    },
    {
      "start": 1218.208,
      "end": 1219.28,
      "text": "That's a hell of a swell system,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1219.34,
      "end": 1219.9,
      "text": "or will be"
    },
    {
      "start": 1220.34,
      "end": 1223.62,
      "text": "when I can give somebody else the bump and hang Thursby's on them."
    },
    {
      "start": 1224.58,
      "end": 1226.2,
      "text": "How long am I supposed to keep that up?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1227.3,
      "end": 1228.94,
      "text": "Are you going to put your hand on my shoulder",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1229.06,
      "end": 1231.54,
      "text": "for all the killings in San Francisco from now on?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1232.8,
      "end": 1233.2,
      "text": "Tom said:",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1233.46,
      "end": 1233.56,
      "text": "\"Aw,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1234.14,
      "end": 1235.12,
      "text": "cut the comedy,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1235.24,
      "end": 1235.42,
      "text": "Sam."
    },
    {
      "start": 1236.06,
      "end": 1238.94,
      "text": "You know damned well we don't like this any more than you do,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1239.28,
      "end": 1240.7,
      "text": "but we got our work to do.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1241.14,
      "end": 1244.76,
      "text": "\"I hope you've got something to do besides pop in here early"
    },
    {
      "start": 1244.92,
      "end": 1246.54,
      "text": "every morning with a lot of damned fool"
    },
    {
      "start": 1246.54,
      "end": 1249.54,
      "text": "questions and get damned lying answers,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1249.82,
      "end": 1251.04,
      "text": "Dundy added deliberately."
    },
    {
      "start": 1252.0,
      "end": 1252.66,
      "text": "\"Take it easy,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1252.98,
      "end": 1254.44,
      "text": "Spade cautioned him."
    },
    {
      "start": 1255.392,
      "end": 1258.02,
      "text": "Dundy looked him up and down and then looked him straight in",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1258.12,
      "end": 1258.32,
      "text": "the eyes."
    },
    {
      "start": 1258.66,
      "end": 1261.66,
      "text": "\"If you say there was nothing between you and Archer's wife,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1261.76,
      "end": 1262.08,
      "text": "he said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1262.26,
      "end": 1263.34,
      "text": "\"you're a liar,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1263.5,
      "end": 1264.86,
      "text": "and I'm telling you so.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1265.18,
      "end": 1268.42,
      "text": "A startled look came into Tom's small eyes."
    },
    {
      "start": 1269.536,
      "end": 1270.94,
      "text": "Spade moistened his lips with",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1270.94,
      "end": 1272.28,
      "text": "the tip of his tongue and asked:"
    },
    {
      "start": 1272.98,
      "end": 1276.54,
      "text": "\"Is that the hot tip that brought you here at this ungodly time"
    },
    {
      "start": 1276.54,
      "end": 1277.0,
      "text": "of night?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1278.24,
      "end": 1279.02,
      "text": "\"That's one of them.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1280.08,
      "end": 1280.6,
      "text": "\"And the others?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1281.824,
      "end": 1283.48,
      "text": "Dundy pulled down the corners of his mouth.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1283.62,
      "end": 1284.58,
      "text": "\"Let us in.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1284.74,
      "end": 1287.84,
      "text": "He nodded significantly at the doorway in which Spade stood."
    },
    {
      "start": 1288.864,
      "end": 1290.18,
      "text": "Spade frowned and shook his head.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1291.36,
      "end": 1294.06,
      "text": "Dundy's mouth-corners lifted in a smile of grim satisfaction.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1295.24,
      "end": 1296.64,
      "text": "\"There must've been something to it,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1296.84,
      "end": 1297.48,
      "text": "he told Tom."
    },
    {
      "start": 1298.624,
      "end": 1301.54,
      "text": "Tom shifted his feet and, not looking at either man, mumbled:",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1302.18,
      "end": 1302.62,
      "text": "\"God knows.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1304.064,
      "end": 1304.46,
      "text": "\"What's this?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1304.66,
      "end": 1305.56,
      "text": "Spade asked."
    },
    {
      "start": 1305.8,
      "end": 1306.55,
      "text": "\"Charades?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1307.78,
      "end": 1308.14,
      "text": "\"All right,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1308.14,
      "end": 1308.64,
      "text": "Spade,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1308.66,
      "end": 1309.24,
      "text": "we're going,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1309.44,
      "end": 1311.12,
      "text": "Dundy buttoned his overcoat."
    },
    {
      "start": 1312.02,
      "end": 1313.44,
      "text": "\"We'll be in to see you now and then.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1314.1,
      "end": 1315.38,
      "text": "Maybe you're right in bucking us."
    },
    {
      "start": 1315.82,
      "end": 1316.28,
      "text": "Think it over.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1317.28,
      "end": 1317.6,
      "text": "\"Uh-huh,\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1317.8,
      "end": 1318.54,
      "text": "Spade said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1318.64,
      "end": 1319.08,
      "text": "grinning."
    },
    {
      "start": 1319.7,
      "end": 1320.86,
      "text": "\"Glad to see you any time,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1320.92,
      "end": 1321.18,
      "text": "Lieutenant,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1321.7,
      "end": 1322.84,
      "text": "and whenever I'm not busy"
    },
    {
      "start": 1322.96,
      "end": 1323.68,
      "text": "I'll let you in.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1324.76,
      "end": 1326.36,
      "text": "A voice in Spade's living-room screamed:",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1326.9,
      "end": 1327.26,
      "text": "\"Help!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1327.42,
      "end": 1327.8,
      "text": "Help!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1327.98,
      "end": 1328.34,
      "text": "Police!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1328.5,
      "end": 1328.76,
      "text": "Help!\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1329.58,
      "end": 1329.9,
      "text": "The voice,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1330.0,
      "end": 1331.08,
      "text": "high and thin and shrill,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1331.16,
      "end": 1332.11,
      "text": "was Joel Cairo's."
    },
    {
      "start": 1333.28,
      "end": 1335.42,
      "text": "Lieutenant Dundy stopped turning away from the door,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1336.0,
      "end": 1336.86,
      "text": "confronted Spade again,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1336.92,
      "end": 1337.88,
      "text": "and said decisively:"
    },
    {
      "start": 1338.56,
      "end": 1339.58,
      "text": "\"I guess we're going in.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1340.02,
      "end": 1341.88,
      "text": "The sounds of a brief struggle,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1342.06,
      "end": 1342.82,
      "text": "of a blow,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1343.44,
      "end": 1345.16,
      "text": "of a subdued cry, came to them."
    },
    {
      "start": 1346.016,
      "end": 1348.62,
      "text": "Spade's face twisted into a smile that held little joy.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1349.18,
      "end": 1349.54,
      "text": "He said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1349.74,
      "end": 1350.82,
      "text": "\"I guess you are,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1351.02,
      "end": 1352.58,
      "text": "and stood out of the way."
    },
    {
      "start": 1353.66,
      "end": 1355.12,
      "text": "When the police-detectives had entered,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1355.34,
      "end": 1358.72,
      "text": "he shut the corridor-door and followed them back to the living-room."
    },
    {
      "start": 1359.744,
      "end": 1360.78,
      "text": "End of chapter seven."
    }
  ]
}
